---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Ketter Home Improvements
description: Ketter Home Improvements provides reliable repair, maintenance, and improvement services in Cleveland, Tennessee and surrounding areas.
permalink: /index.html
---

<main class="page-wrap">
  <div class="site-shell">
    <section class="home-intro-card card-block">
      <div class="card-block-body">
        <h1 class="home-title mb-3">Reliable repair, maintenance, and improvement services.</h1>
        <p class="lead-text mb-3">
          We help homeowners and property owners with practical repairs, ongoing maintenance, and straightforward improvement work in Cleveland, Tennessee and surrounding areas.
        </p>
        <p class="support-text mb-4">
          Text communication is preferred. If you are contacting us about a project, completing the service request form is the best way to send the details.
        </p>

        <div class="action-grid">
          <a href="/service-request.html" class="action-card action-card-primary">
            <span class="action-card-title">Request Service</span>
            <span class="action-card-text">Best way to send project details.</span>
          </a>

          <a href="/portal/sign-in/" class="action-card">
            <span class="action-card-title">Project Center</span>
            <span class="action-card-text">Sign in to view project information.</span>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-strip">
          <div class="contact-strip-item">
            <span class="contact-label">Call or text</span>
            <a href="tel:{{ site.phone_href }}">{{ site.phone_display }}</a>
            <div class="contact-note">{{ site.contact_preference }}</div>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-strip-item">
            <span class="contact-label">Email</span>
            <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-strip-item">
            <span class="contact-label">Service Area</span>
            <span>{{ site.service_area }}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h2>Services</h2>
        <p>
          We focus on practical work, clear communication, and dependable follow-through.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-grid card-grid-3">
        <div class="card-block">
          <div class="card-block-body">
            <h3>General Repairs</h3>
            <p>Drywall, trim, doors, fixtures, hardware, minor plumbing repairs, and everyday household fixes.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card-block">
          <div class="card-block-body">
            <h3>Property Maintenance</h3>
            <p>Ongoing maintenance for homeowners, landlords, and rental properties to keep things running smoothly.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card-block">
          <div class="card-block-body">
            <h3>Installations</h3>
            <p>Appliance hookups, fixtures, shelving, hardware, and other basic home installation projects.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card-block">
          <div class="card-block-body">
            <h3>Interior Improvements</h3>
            <p>Small upgrades that improve function, appearance, and value without overcomplicating the process.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card-block">
          <div class="card-block-body">
            <h3>Rental Turnover Work</h3>
            <p>Punch-list items, touch-ups, repairs, and readying properties for new tenants.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card-block">
          <div class="card-block-body">
            <h3>Custom Requests</h3>
            <p>Have a project in mind? Send the details and we will let you know if it is a good fit.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="card-grid card-grid-2">
        <div class="card-block">
          <div class="card-block-body">
            <h2>Why work with us</h2>
            <ul class="plain-list">
              <li>Clear communication</li>
              <li>Dependable scheduling</li>
              <li>Practical solutions</li>
              <li>Quality workmanship</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card-block">
          <div class="card-block-body">
            <h2>How to contact us</h2>
            <p><strong>Text is usually the fastest way to reach us.</strong></p>
            <p>Clients can choose the contact method that works best for them, but completing the service request form is highly encouraged when sending project details.</p>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong>Call or text:</strong> <a href="tel:{{ site.phone_href }}">{{ site.phone_display }}</a></p>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a></p>
            <p class="mb-0"><strong>Service area:</strong> {{ site.service_area }}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</main>